* Workspace-Level Entitlements
** Unrestricted cluster creation
***_ Allows non-admins to create clusters
***_ No size restrictions
***_ Does NOT grant workspace admin
** Default behavior
***_ Only admins can create any-size cluster
** Grant via Settings
***_ Identity and access > Users/Groups
***_ Entitlements section
***_ Enable "Allow cluster creation"
** Grant to roles/teams, not individuals
** Principle of least privilege
***_ Data engineers: may need it
***_ Analysts: usually don't need it
@endmindmap
